  "authoritative_product_boundary": "Tirzepatide is the active substance in exact authorised MOUNJARO and ZEPBOUND products. The current ZEPBOUND label covers chronic weight management and moderate-to-severe obstructive sleep apnoea in adults with obesity. Catalogue TR powders do not inherit any authorised product's formulation, pen system, concentration, quality or indication.",
  "human_evidence_boundary": "SURMOUNT-1 was a phase 3 randomised trial in 2,539 adults with obesity or overweight and a weight-related complication without diabetes. Product-specific trials and labels also support other exact indications. None validates catalogue lyophilised vials.",
  "safety_source_boundary": "Current label controls include thyroid C-cell tumour warning, severe gastrointestinal reactions, acute kidney injury from volume depletion, gallbladder disease, pancreatitis, hypersensitivity, hypoglycaemia with relevant concomitant medicines, diabetic-retinopathy complications, pregnancy risk and pulmonary aspiration during anaesthesia or deep sedation.",
